snippet.title: MMX Hill Dash 2 - OUT NOW!!!
snippet.description:
MMX Hill Dash 2

The sequel to the hugely popular MMX Hill Dash. Available for Android and iOS. Insane physics racing brought to you by Hutch - the makers of Top Drives, MMX Racing, Hot Wheels Race Off and many other racing favourites on mobile.
